- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses neural-attention based sequence-to-sequence models, which are a popular technique in AI research. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also possible as the paper discusses training models on large amounts of data and adapting models to different output sizes.
